But she's already revealed her hand,
so it's considered a Trick Hand

1397
01:26:48,460 --> 01:26:50,460
- Yes - We are at the last round

1398
01:26:50,570 --> 01:26:52,800
and it's a tie between
Deedee Zhang and Sassy Ba

1399
01:26:52,900 --> 01:26:54,730
Deedee's Trick Hand causes her

