number one in anything else

1412
01:27:40,520 --> 01:27:43,280
I only want you to be number one in mahjong

1413
01:27:44,120 --> 01:27:46,820
Since I'm such an embarassment
to you, I'll leave

1414
01:27:47,160 --> 01:27:48,650
You're leaving…

1415
01:27:48,730 --> 01:27:51,560
Who's gonna take photo
with me later when I win?

1416
01:27:52,430 --> 01:27:54,920
You'd ruin my perfect father image

1417
01:27:58,070 --> 01:27:59,660
If she really leaves

1418
01:27:59,740 --> 01:28:02,860
Cancel all her credit cards for me

1419
01:28:06,640 --> 01:28:09,540
The most exciting match
and the best of the best

